title: The Truth Behind The Sway House Breakup- BFFs Ep 27 with Whitney Cummings
description:
The crew is back together. We watch the latest Lil Huddy music video, get clarity on the real reason Sway broke up, and Logan Paul's reaction to Alex Cooper exposing him. Comedian Whitney Cummings comes on the second half of the show to talk about her thoughts on the Tik Tok world.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
